randombg, a command tool for switching desktop backgrounds with 'feh'. ( You have to install 'feh' first. )
randombg will search whole disk for all suitable images, then take one for your desktop background every other minutes according to randombg_config.
You can set directory, image size, interval time, and sound on/off.

randombg is made by www.lulinux.com. Thank you for visiting my blog!

Usage:
randombg <full_dir_path> [-wset|-w2560|-w1920|-w1680|-w1440|-w1366|-w1280|-w1024|-w800] [-iset|-i240|-i120|-i60|-i30|-i15|-i0]
         Three parameters are optional. If no parameter, I'll call randombg config file. 
         full_dir_path What image dir to use. If the path isn't in randombg_list, I'll ask to update db. 
         -wset Use images whose width >= the number that you input .
         -w2560 Use images whose width >= 2560 pixels.
         -w1920 Use images whose width >= 1920 pixels.
         -w1680 Use images whose width >= 1680 pixels.
         -w1440 Use images whose width >= 1440 pixels.
         -w1366 Use images whose width >= 1366 pixels.
         -w1280 Use images whose width >= 1280 pixels.
         -w1024 Use images whose width >= 1024 pixels.
         -w800 Use images whose width >= 800 pixels.This is default.
         -iset Set interval time to a number that you input.
         -i240 Set interval time to 240 minutes.
         -i120 Set interval time to 120 minutes.
         -i60 Set interval time to 60 minutes.
         -i30 Set interval time to 30 minutes.
         -i15 Set interval time to 15 minutes.
         -i0 Set interval time to 0.This is default.
randombg [-c|--configure]
         Configure directory, image width and interval time.
randombg [-u|--updatedb]
         Update randombg_list from whold disk.
randombg --list-all
         List all image files in randombg_list.
randombg [-l|--list-current]
         List current image files you'll use.
randombg --show-config
         Show configuration.
randombg --sound-on
         Play sound when switching background.
randombg --sound-off
         Do not play sound when switching background.
randombg [-h|--help]
         Show this help.
randombg [-v|--version]
         Show version.


